A BILL ENTITLED
1 AN ACT concerning
2 Municipalities – Annexation Resolutions – Submission to Department of
3 Planning
4 FOR the purpose of adding the Department of Planning to the list of entities to which a
5 municipality must send a copy of an annexation resolution with the new municipal
6 boundaries; and generally relating to municipal annexation resolutions.
7 BY repealing and reenacting, with amendments,
8 Article – Local Government
9 Section 4–414
